Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:03.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:12.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:17.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:20.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,turned to rubber after \Nhe ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:35.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and were drawn into a climactic \Nbattle on Punk Hazard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhich ended with Caesar's capture.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:42.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, they headed out\Nfor their next destination - Dressrosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:45.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}along with their pirate \Nally - the Warlord - Law.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:49.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the course of their \Ntrip, they were attacked by
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the Breed Pirates who were \Nlooking to get hold of Caesar{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but they defeated them \Nafter a great struggle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don Quixote Doflamingo..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...Withdraws from..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...the Seven Warlords"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Startling!\NThe Big News Shakes Up the New World!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Withdraws from the Seven Warlords"?\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I know? Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressrosa is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All tall waves were originally...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...little waves, barely worthy of notice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's gonna happen to the arms deal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbetween Don Quixote family and us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to reach them\Nbut nobody picks up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe this!\NWe will lose the war without arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those reckless rookies from two years ago\Nformed an alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're up to something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo resigned from the Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he do that?!\NIsn't there anymore information?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Get more information!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they find out about our alliance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this freelance writer named Absa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gets scoops very often these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about us.\NI'm more concerned about the other news.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat and Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're looking to take out\None of the Four Emperors like we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is their target?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring... Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.\NI resigned from the Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He picked up!\N--Picked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? I'm Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Mingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid, old Caesar's boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHe gave Brownbeard and the children hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will give you back Caesar as we promised\Nbut if you do that again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will beat the hell out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You went away for two years\Nafter your brother died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where were you\Nand what were you doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't tell anyone about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to see you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have something\Nthat you'll want very badly now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something... that I'll want...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,â€¦very badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How delicious is that meat \Nyou're talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}!\NDon't get drawn into his pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One chunk of meat! Two chunks of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThis is a special attack called "His Pace"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred chunks of meat!\NTwo hundred chunks of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Don't get drawn into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker! Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hand Caesar over to you as we promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, that's for your own good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you try to run away with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:55.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nyou know what will happen to you guys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:08:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, can I hear my precious \Nbusiness partner's voice?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You resigned from the Warlords for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, he sounded fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight hours from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the beach on the southeast \Nside of Green Bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe solitary island north of Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will leave Caesar there\Nat three in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and pick him up.\NAnd this will all be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.\NI wish I could have a drink with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just hang up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost got drawn into his pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes! Your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWe didn't tell him how many men he can bring!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"How many men"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do\Nif he brings his entire crew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The handover of Caesar is a part of our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIt's just to lure them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, destroying a \NSMILE manufacturing factory
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhile it's unguarded is our main purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But we don't know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Factories are big. You can barely miss them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get there, we'll {\i1}super{\i0} find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.41,0:09:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy it with my laser beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have intelligence on \Neverything but the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIt's an important asset for them, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, there is a secret to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you're gonna \Ngo to Green Bit earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will dock this ship at Dressrosa.\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy, have you been to that island?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dress-{\i1}roba{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dress-roba (old woman)?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "rosa"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that bastard's kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's figure everything out\Nonce we get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be an adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait to see Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go to the Wano Kingdom soon, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NYou can't just show up without a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we have for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I want a cotton-candy sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A glass of milk for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the best breakfast in the world is\NSanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you why we were being chased.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we set sail for the \Nplace called Zou originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's another coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After handing over Caesar\Nand destroying the SMILE factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna head for Zou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my crew is already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If so, can we go along with you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you can! Let's go there\Nand then the Wano Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0}, thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Tra-guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three samurais including me, and Momonosuke -
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nfour of us headed for Zou
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but our ship wrecked
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and two of us samurais and Momonosuke\Ndrifted to Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we had been chased by\NDoflamingo and the others there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I ran into an unknown ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, I met the children\Nwho were looking to get treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And unfortunately, the ship left the port
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I knew it and headed for that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Father!\N--Oh no! Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna go after the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my fellow samurai Kanjuro tried\Nto cover me but got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go after Momonosuke! Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He let me sail out to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a man, Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'm gonna go save him with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Don't forget our purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0},\NTrÃ©bol-{\i1}sama{\i0} is not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:28.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NAVY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:41.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE NAVY HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only seven Warlords in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the pirates who \Nwere chosen and given
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the carte blanche for robbery \Nby the World Government
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in exchange for their overwhelming strength\Nand notorious prestige!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Them taking sides with \Nthe Government has to be
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seen as a threat to all \Nother pirates in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest swordsman in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hawk-Eye" Dracule Mihawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king of Dressrosa \Nand a charismatic devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Heavenly Demon" Don Quixote Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is now the Navy's human weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tyrant" Bartholomew Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The empress of Amazon Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pirate Empress" Boa Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Worst Generation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand the mastermind of the Rocky Port Incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Surgeon of Death" Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this man has become powerful rapidly\Nin last two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Pirate Dispatch Organization\Nand a living legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Star Clown" Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you surprised that I'm a Warlord?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I wanted to become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government begged me in tears
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I accepted reluctantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is only the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop me from advancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna join the Four \NEmperors in a few years!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NAnd I'm gonna become the King of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the man I told you about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThey are the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that all changed early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo resigned out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we might need to expel Law
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the Warlords depending on his intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together, they're one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Great Powers along with the \NNavy HQ and the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things shouldn't be so unstable...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know, Brandnew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleet Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let Law and Straw Hat\Ndo whatever they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got an annoying call from\NSmoker of the G-5 yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how things go for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent Fujitora!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true what they say on the newspaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us it's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TrÃ©bol-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TrÃ©bol-{\i1}sama{\i0}, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen TrÃ©bol-{\i1}sama{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Young \NMaster-{\i1}sama{\i0} is going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Navy is gonna come to attack,\NI want to fight-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will just follow the Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TrÃ©bol-{\i1}sama{\i0}, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Baby 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The whole kingdom is going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the whole world is getting upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you get \Nyour fiancÃ© killed again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep asking me that?\NYou're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying but?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying but what? Hmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annoying but you like me, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!\NYoung Master-{\i1}sama{\i0} was calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted you to bring {\i1}that thing{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away! You make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NYou just keep getting your fiancÃ© killed! Baby 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop choosing guys that would \Nbe killed by Doffy and marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...need me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colosseum is always packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, Diamante.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy, that's because \Nyou're a charismatic king.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. You make it sound like\NI'm the hero of the Colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} the hero of the Colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I admit it if you insist!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am the hero of the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy, it's {\i1}that thing{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too close but?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like it. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Straw Hat Luffy finds out about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI'm sure he will try to get hold of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An alliance can sometimes prove a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamante. I want to entrust this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second, Doffy! I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want to entrust this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. You make it sound like\NI'm some kind of genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only entrust this to a genius like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I admit that I'm \Na genius if you insist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I can take care of \Nthat dumb-ass Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know he will jump at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The source of his late brother's power.\NThe Flare-Flare Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he wouldn't want \Nanybody else to have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.87,0:22:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Straw Hats see a shadow of an island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that rocky island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:22:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it! It's Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't shout!\NDoflamingo will hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll save you soon, Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.92,0:23:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a kingdom of love \Nand passion - Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
